name: TechSF
description: Free technology job training and tech industry career placement
fullDescription: TechSF provides free technology job training and placement services for San Francisco residents seeking careers in the tech industry.
whatTheyOffer:
- Free tech skills training
- Coding bootcamp scholarships
- IT support certifications
- Job placement assistance
- Internship connections
- Career mentorship
howToGetIt:
1. Visit TechSF website
2. Complete interest form
3. Attend orientation session
4. Apply for training programs
5. Receive job placement support
keywords: TechSF, San Francisco, free tech training, coding bootcamp, IT certifications, tech career, job placement, internship, career mentorship
